{"tid":857221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點先可以令港豬醒覺","createTime":"2018-10-11T03:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T05:15:50.000Z","uid":134294,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5228c9411af8bd86e18dcc96c09929a3279b7479","tid":857221,"uid":134294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:32:10.000Z","msg":"當你地話梁天琦，黃之峰嗰啲冇事搵事嚟搞<br />\n唔支持佢地都算，話曬每個舞都有唔同政治取向<br />\n但係喺呢幾年啲大白象工程個個超支不特止<br />\n仲要係偷工減料<br />\n又減醫療開支<br />\n啲人都可以當冇事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦而家話要用一萬億去整個可有可冇嘅人工島都好似冇乜反對聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣馬照跑舞照跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n林鄭一定心諗正呀，下次整多個幾萬億project先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟而家係唔係無可能再好似雨傘運動咁一班人反政府<br />\n只可以慢慢等到2047<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc314a4dc9347912f109fe1974b1c07e75299bec","tid":857221,"uid":71543,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"你無法叫醒一個裝睡的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf33b85e5fda4b9331c9dad7a929e4a7bde9e1a2","tid":857221,"uid":106954,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔洗爭 其實個個都係港豬"},{"pid":"1ded9b51375db68a5874d8553486d841dd3f15cc","tid":857221,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"成日話醒覺醒覺, 點為之醒覺???"},{"pid":"c40a47893bbe44443bd4cbfe7e1a725512bcc1cf","tid":857221,"uid":134294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ded9b51375db68a5874d8553486d841dd3f15cc","tid":857221,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"成日話醒覺醒覺, 點為之醒覺???"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:50:27.000Z","msg":"起碼會留意社會問題、時事<br />\n唔係剩係識話要返工，不了先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /